title: Counter Strike - Condition Zero (Ultimate Edition) (spiderot sha
description:
Watch this for game view and play

simple and no key required

installation is simple next->next->next 
after clicking the file it takes time for the installation to start so dont worry be patient 
it may show as corrupted while installing but it is not and works great(trust me)

win7 may need compatibility put to vista or xp in settings (if any problem comes in terms of resolution or such)

for multi player lan play un-block the game in the firewall before play

this game includes many maps and comes with different maps with in the game and also has Bot add and difficulty level setings

this pack also has the halflife game pack within it enjoy
